General Information

Hemp Seed Oil 1,100mg - 100s

Warnings

Always read the label. Take only as directed. If taking prescription medication or if in doubt, talk to your health professional. Contains: Soya bean products and sulfites

Common Uses

Hemp Seed oil provides a balanced source of omega essential fatty acids. This formula contains extra virgin, cold pressed, organic Hemp Seed oil supplied in the convenience of a capsule.

Ingredients

INGREDIENTS: Each soft capsule contains: Hemp Seed Oil (73%), Gelatin, Glycerol, Water, Antioxidant (d-alpha tocopherol).

Directions

DIRECTIONS FOR USE: Take 1-3 soft capsules daily, best taken with food.
